t lower redshifts ($z\\sim 0$), an SFR of $\\sim 1$ M$_\\odot$ yr$^{-1}$\ncan suppress the infall into galaxies of mass $\\le 10^{10}$ M$_\\odot$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jun 2018 18:01:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-31"}
