 $a(\\omega)$ and $a_0(t)$ are bounded above and below\nby some positive constants. The results obtained in this part are new and\nextend the existing results in literature on spreading speeds of Fisher-KPP\nequations. In the second part of the series, we will study the existence and\nstability of transition fronts of (1) and (2).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jun 2018 19:56:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Mar 2020 18:25:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-10"}
