 these observations, we expect that the fascinating pairing with\nrelatively high $T_{\\rm c}$ emerges at high doping that involves all the three\nFermi pockets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2018 00:47:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-29"}
