antity is a valid observable that can shed light on the relative\nimportance of mergers and stellar stripping for the formation of the ICL.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2018 03:32:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Jul 2018 03:49:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-04"}
