t later evolutionary stages. This confirms that ambipolar\ndiffusion is an important process for diffuse gas, but becomes less significant\nas cores collapse to higher densities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2018 14:04:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-25"}
