WPs, especially $HFO1234ze$ which is not flammable at room temperature.\nSeveral tests on $HFO$-based mixtures with addition of various gases are\nongoing and encouraging results have already been obtained. Furthermore, the\nuse of $CO_{2}$ as a quencher has been studied as it might represent a valid\nsolution to avoid flammability of the mixture. Finally, medium-term stability\nof detectors exposed to the cosmic-ray flux will be shown in this paper.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2018 15:24:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-29"}
